org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute

Class PaAttributeValueFactoryIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute.PaAttributeValueFactoryIetf

  • public final class PaAttributeValueFactoryIetf
extends Object
    Factory utility to create an IETF RFC 5792 compliant integrity measurement attribute value.
